data.description: Price Reduced to Sell on this beautiful South Bossier Custom Home Built in Golden Meadows. Hardwood In Living And Master Bedroom. Ceramic Floors In Bathrooms And Kitchen, Granite Counters In Both. Beautiful large Kitchen with Stainless Steel Appliances  and Slide Out Custom Microwave. Large Master Bedroom with ensuite and two walk-in closets. Oversized Master Bath Shower With Body Jets And Bench. Giant Jacuzzi In Master. Custom Slate Stone Fireplace. Fully fenced-in backyard with a covered patio to enjoy time outside - conveniently located near BAFB, South Bossier schools, local shopping and dining.
